    <item>
      <title>马赫卢夫称尚不清楚欧洲央行将以多快的速度继续行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/makhlouf-says-it-s-unclear-how-fast-ecb-will-carry-on-if-at-all</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员加布里埃尔·马赫卢夫表示，由于通胀前景仍不确定，目前尚不清楚欧洲央行何时会再次降低利率——或者是否会降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/makhlouf-says-it-s-unclear-how-fast-ecb-will-carry-on-if-at-all</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 07:46:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通指数发布日期临近，印度储备创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/india-s-reserves-hit-record-as-jpmorgan-index-date-draws-near</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于外国投资者在印度债券被纳入摩根大通旗舰新兴市场债务指数之前纷纷购买印度债券，印度的外汇储备上周增至 6515 亿美元的历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/india-s-reserves-hit-record-as-jpmorgan-index-date-draws-near</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 06:34:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
