    <item>
      <title>债券持有人就瑞士信贷 AT1 债券在美国起诉瑞士</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bondholders-sue-switzerland-in-us-over-credit-suisse-at1-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团在瑞士政府的斡旋下拯救了瑞士信贷集团，导致该银行的债券投资者损失惨重。现在，他们正在纽约对瑞士提起诉讼，并将诉讼范围扩大到国外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/bondholders-sue-switzerland-in-us-over-credit-suisse-at1-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 17:33:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
