      <title>吉普制造商考虑在南非生产新能源汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/jeep-maker-considers-producing-new-energy-vehicles-in-south-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Stellantis NV 将于本月在南非开始建造其第一家汽车厂，该公司正考虑在南非扩大所谓的新能源汽车生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/jeep-maker-considers-producing-new-energy-vehicles-in-south-africa</guid>
